A subscriber to the <talk at gtalug.org> email was being used to forward
support tickets to a JIRA instances (you might have received an email
from "Service Desk" or "Advanced Service Desk". If I don't receive an
email from this message the problem should be fixed.

Please don't turn this into the Salem witch trials as it looks to be an
honest mistake.

Have an awesome day, and happy open-sourcing :-).

